                  <collation>
                     <p>The quires, 20 in number, are signed with both letters and arithmetical figures (e.g. <locus from="82a" to="82a">fol. 82 a</locus>, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܛ</foreign> and <!-- NEEDS ARABIC -->).</p>
