                    <locus from="200b" to="200b"/>
                    <p>On fol. 200 b, at the end of <ref target="#p2a1">the Gospel of S. John</ref>, there is a note, unfortunately mutilated, stating that these two leaves were written by one <persName ref="">Gabriel of Edessa</persName>:</p>
                    <p><quote xml:lang="syr">ܨܠܘ ܥܠ ܚܛܝܐ . . . ܓܒܪܝܠ ܒܪ ܡـ . . . ܐ ܩܝܢܝܐ ܡܢ ܐܘܪܗܝ ܡـ[ܕܝܢܬܐ ܪܚܡܬ] ܠܡܫܝܚܐ ܕܢܚܣܐ ܠܗ ܡܪܝܐ ܘ . . . ܘܝܐ ܘܠܟܬܘܒܐ ܘ܏ܫ.</quote></p>
